CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1973, pg. 10 reads: "Ribbon Cutting - Jim David cuts ribbon of the new Shop-N-Save Super Market at 566 Brushton Avenue in Homewood, as Bob Buczkowski, manager, extreme right, and others look on. Left to right, Jacqueline Jones, Velma Adams, Norma Blakey, Bill Broadus, Mr. Davis, Pam Montgomery, Jim Whalen and Mr. Buczkowski. (Harris Photo)
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Jacqueline Jones, Velma Adams, Norma Blakey, Bill Broadus, Jim Davis cutting ribbon, Pam Montgomery, Jim Whalen, and Bob Buczkowski, gathered for opening of Shop-N-Save Supermarket, 566 Brushton Avenue, Homewood
